{"title":"青蒲","authors":["陈加正"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":9,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蒲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈加正"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蒲生长的地方很小很窄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但那里可是孩子们的乐园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们在蒲丛中可以玩藏猫猫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以执一柄青蒲剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"演他们自编自导的“抓奸贼”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且他们个个都会唱“青蒲歌”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会唱——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月五日五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈公骑艾虎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手持蒲蒲剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱魔归地府"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那调门很好听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很有点青蒲微熏熏的味道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折一截青蒲也可以作笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以“嘟嘟”地吹出南方的亲切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你听见哪儿有蒲笛和青蒲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌悠悠地飘出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里就准会有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于《离骚》、关于青蒲剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最初最初的传说"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}